bookedbyus inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Technology
Industry: Software
Sub-Industry: Application Software
Bookedbyus Inc.  is a development stage company. The Company  intends to develop and market software applications licensed from another company. Bookedbyus offers a web and email based media application that allows clients to push media marketing material to its customers with a fully integrated back end including business analytics.




