Apawthecary Pets USA: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 12:42 AM ET
Diversified Consumer Services

Company Overview of Apawthecary Pets USA



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Apawthecary Pets USA, a development stage company, intends to operate in the pet industry. The company was formerly known as Bookedbyus, Inc. and changed its name to Apawthecary Pets USA in April 2017. Apawthecary Pets USA was founded in 2007 and is based in Lake Tahoe, Nevada.


619 South Ridgeley DriveSuite 101Los Angeles, CA 90036United StatesFounded in 2007



Phone: 323-634-1000








Key Executives for Apawthecary Pets USA




