Compensation as of Fiscal Year 2017. 

Apawthecary Pets USA Key Developments

Bookedbyus Inc. announced delayed 10-Q filing
Jul 17 17
On 07/17/2017, Bookedbyus Inc. announced that they will be unable to file their next 10-Q by the deadline required by the SEC.


Bookedbyus Inc. Announces Management Changes
Mar 20 17
Effective February 24, 2017, Fred Person resigned from his position as President and Director of Bookedbyus Inc. Mr. Persons' resignation is not the result of any disagreement with the company on any matter relating to the company's operations, policies or practices. Effective February 24, 2017 the Board approved by unanimous written consent the appointment of Bradley Kersch and Aerock Fox as President and Director, Secretary and Director respectively for the company.


Bookedbyus Inc. Auditor Raises 'Going Concern' Doubt
Dec 5 16
Bookedbyus Inc. filed its 10-K on Dec 05, 2016 for the period ending Aug 31, 2016. In this report its auditor, Malone & Bailey, PLLC, gave an unqualified opinion expressing doubt that the company can continue as a going concern.


