RENO, NV  89509-7020  United States







Business Summary




Bookedbyus Inc. is a development stage company. The Company is a licensed distributor for Digital Programa Inc. (DP). It focuses on developing and marketing two software applications licensed from DP, eDrive and iDrive. eDrive is a Web and e-mail-based media application that enables clients to push media marketing material to its customers. eDrive, enables companies to market their message or product directly to their customers. As of August 31, 2010, the Company had not generated any revenue. DP develops digital media management and workflow automation system software for the entertainment business. DP has developed an online digital collaboration management system that corporations who create and distribute media (photo, audio and video, as well as other digital assets like documents), find, organize, share, distribute, store and view such media.


